  <arm_group>
    <arm_group_label>BIS 55</arm_group_label>
    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>Induction:
TCI propofol (6 µg/ml) - remifentanil (4 ng/ml) Atracurium IV (0.5 mg/kg)
Orotracheal Intubation
Remifentanil target decreased to 1 ng/ml
Propofol target adjustment to reach BIS 55
10 minutes steady state
Tetanic stimulation (ulnar nerve): 100 Hz, 60 milliamps, 5 seconds
Pupillary dilation recording (videopupillometer Algiscan)</description>
